'''Rocksteady Studios'''是一間位於[[倫敦|倫敦]]高門（Highgate）的[[英國|英國]]電子遊戲開發商。他們的遊戲有《{{le|混沌都市：骚乱回应|Urban Chaos: Riot Response}}》、《[[蝙蝠俠：阿卡姆瘋人院|蝙蝠俠：阿卡姆瘋人院]]》、《[[蝙蝠俠：阿卡姆之城|蝙蝠俠：阿卡姆之城]]》和《[[蝙蝠俠：阿卡姆騎士|蝙蝠俠：阿卡姆騎士]]》。截至2014年，公司擁有149名員工，下設12個部門<ref name="Rocksteady_Stats">{{cite web |url=http://rocksteadyltd.com/#stats |title=Rocksteady Welcome to Rocksteady Studios |publisher=Rocksteady Studios |accessdate=2014-07-12 |language=en |archive-date=2014-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104121932/http://rocksteadyltd.com/#stats |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="IGN">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/companies/rocksteady-studios |title=Rocksteady Studios Games |website= |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2014-07-12 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809085536/http://www.ign.com/companies/rocksteady-studios |archivedate=2014-08-09 }}</ref>。

== 歷史 ==
Rocksteady Studios於2004年由Sefton Hill和Jamie Walker創立，他們分別是[[Argonaut_Games|Argonaut Games]]的前製作總監和創意總監。工作室成立後，他們聘請了一些Argonaut Games前員工<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/roll-call-back-on-track-as-sci-funds-new-development-studio|title=SCi funds new development studio|last=Fahey|first=Rob|publisher=[[Eurogamer#GamesIndustry.biz|GamesIndustry.biz]]|date=2005-01-17|accessdate=2008-07-22|archive-date=2012-07-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699xXzrZO?url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/roll-call-back-on-track-as-sci-funds-new-development-studio|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="IGN"/>。

2010年2月，[[時代華納|時代華納]]購入其大多數股份，將其收購。收購後，[[史克威尔艾尼克斯歐洲|史克威尔艾尼克斯歐洲]]（前身為[[Eidos_Interactive|Eidos Interactive]]）仍擁有其25.1%的股份<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5477933/warner-buys-batman-arkham-asylum-devs|title=Warner Buys Batman: Arkham Asylum Devs|last=Plunkett|first=Luke|publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|date=2010-02-23|accessdate=2012-09-04|archive-date=2012-07-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699xYtSUO?url=http://kotaku.com/5477933/warner-buys-batman-arkham-asylum-devs|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Ludwig Kietzmann |title=Warner Bros. acquires Batman dev Rocksteady Studios |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/02/23/warner-bros-acquires-majority-stake-in-rocksteady-studios/ |publisher=Joystiq |date=2010-02-23 |accessdate=2014-07-12 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714201751/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/02/23/warner-bros-acquires-majority-stake-in-rocksteady-studios/ |archive-date=2014-07-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2014年3月4日，Rocksteady和華納兄弟公佈了下一款、也是阿卡姆系列的最終作：《蝙蝠俠：阿卡姆騎士》，遊戲將會在[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]上發行。

== 獎項 ==
在2009年Spike電子遊戲獎賞（Spike Video Game Awards）中，Rocksteady Studios被評為年度工作室<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/spike-tv-announces-2009-video-game-awards-winners-79149557.html|title=Spike TV Announces 2009 Video Game Awards Winners|publisher=[[PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]]|accessdate=2012-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121008180818/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/spike-tv-announces-2009-video-game-awards-winners-79149557.html|archive-date=2012-10-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

